    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK956">
<l>calampaṟṟic cārpila ceyyārmā caṟṟa</l>
<l>kulampaṟṟi vāḻtumeṉ pār</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Those who seek to preserve the irreproachable honour of their families will not viciously do what is detrimental thereto.</l>
            </lg>
